sequenceDiagram
  actor U as user
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant BE as Backend
  participant EM as Ollama (Embeddings)
  participant PG as Supabase (pgvector)
  participant AI as KI-Provider-Pool
  U->>FE: Frage im Chat (Deck offen)
  FE->>BE: POST /api/chat/stream  +  Bearer JWT
  BE->>BE: Permission-Check (READ)
  BE->>EM: Frage -> Embedding (nomic-embed-text)
  EM-->>BE: Vektor (768-dim)
  BE->>PG: match_document_chunks (top-k = 5)
  PG-->>BE: relevante Karten-Chunks
  BE->>AI: System-Prompt + Kontext (round-robin)
  AI-->>BE: Antwort-Tokens (Stream)
  BE-->>FE: Antwort-Tokens (Stream)
  FE-->>U: Antwort-Tokens (Stream)
